      "source_kind": "source-snippet",
      "source_repo": "ashvardanian/NumKong",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "Portable mixed-precision math, linear-algebra, & retrieval library with 2'000+ SIMD kernels for x86, Arm, RISC-V, LoongArch, Power, & WebAssembly, leveraging rare algebraic transforms with both 1D & 2D registers like AMX & SME, covering 15+ numeric types from 4-bit integers & 6-\u2026"
    },
    {
